!! # Orthography tags
  +Orth/PhonDeriv !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * Derivation is phonetic but declension and conjugation morphologic
  +Orth/PhonInfl  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * Entire inflection is phonetic 1821, 1920-30
  +Orth/standard  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * described in 2008, dictionary 2012
  +Orth/thirties  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * 1939вАУ1955 phonetic, morphological
  +Orth/fifties  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * 1955вАУ1978 phonetic, morphological
  +Orth/seventies  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * 1978вАУ1993 phonetic, morphological
  +Orth/nineties  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * 1993-2008 morphological, but phonetic compounding
  +Orth/wiki  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * Regular-semantic deriving from 1993 and 2008
  +Orth/-wiki  !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * e.g. compound words written with white space
  +Orth/standard_wiki !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * e.g. –≤–∞–є–≥–µ–ї—М–њ–µ
  +Orth/-thirties !!вЙИ * @CODE@ * e.g. —В–∞—А–≥—Б–µ–Љ—Б, —Б—В—Г–і–µ–љ—В—В–љ—Н
